Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Accurate view on pglogical replication delay
 Periodically churn an in-replication table using a Postgres background worker
 to get replication time from standpoint of pglogical provider.
 This extension helps monitor and measure replication lag in pglogical setups
 by maintaining a ticker table that is continuously updated.